Comic Heroes Issue 21 (WorldMags) - 2013  UK

SOURCE:  WorldMags.net

164 Pages | PDF | English | 110 MB 


Essential reading for life-long fans and newcomers alike, Comic Heroes is the only magazine dedicated to all things comics - everything from graphic novels through to the films and videogames they inspire. It features the best in creator interviews, chats with the stars of blockbuster movies plus comprehensive reviews, as well as practical advice for aspiring writers or artists. Launched less than two years ago, it's created by the people behind best-selling sci-fi title SFX and is now available six times a year.
